OL,3,COfficer facing trial over 'threat
OL,4,Creport' after Troubles memorial
OL,5,Cincident
OL,7,FA PSNI officer is to be prosecuted for
OL,8,Fconspiring to pervert the course of
OL,9,Fjustice in relation to an incident at
OL,10,Fa Troubles commemoration during the
OL,11,FCovid-19 pandemic, the Public
OL,12,FProsecution Service has confirmed.
OL,14,FThe prosecution is linked to events
OL,15,Fthat unfolded on the Ormeau Road in
OL,16,FBelfast in February 2021 during a
OL,17,Fservice marking the anniversary of the
OL,18,FSean Graham bookmakers attack in which
OL,19,Ffive people were murdered and nine
OL,20,Fothers injured by the UFF.
