OL,5,Cincident
OL,7,FTwo officers faced internal
OL,8,Fdisciplinary action after a survivor
OL,9,Fof the 1992 loyalist shooting was
OL,10,Farrested at the memorial.
OL,12,FIt came after police had challenged
OL,13,Fpeople attending amid suspicions that
OL,14,Fthe size of the public gathering
OL,15,Fbreached coronavirus regulations.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
