OL,7,FLast year, a High Court judge found
OL,8,Fthat the disciplinary actions taken
OL,9,Fagainst the two junior police officers
OL,10,Fwere unlawful, and were motivated by a
OL,11,Fdesire by commanders to allay any
OL,12,Fthreat of Sinn Fein abandoning its
OL,13,Fsupport for policing in Northern
OL,14,FIreland.
OL,16,FThe ruling was one of the main
OL,17,Fcontributory factors that led to the
OL,18,Fresignation of former PSNI chief
OL,19,Fconstable Simon Byrne last September.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
