OL,7,FThe prosecution decision announced by
OL,8,Fthe PPS on Wednesday is not directly
OL,9,Flinked to the events on the day of the
OL,10,Fincident in 2021.
OL,12,FThe decision to prosecute the
OL,13,Findividual comes after an
OL,14,Finvestigation by the PSNI's Anti-
OL,15,FCorruption Unit (ACU).
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
