OL,5,Cincident
OL,7,FThe ACU investigation was related to
OL,8,Fan incident on the Ormeau Road on 5
OL,9,FFebruary, 2021 concerning an
OL,10,Fallegation that an officer was
OL,11,Finvolved in a false threat report
OL,12,Fintended to support an application for
OL,13,Fan anonymity order related to the
OL,14,Foriginal incident.
OL,16,FThe individual facing the charge has
OL,17,Fbeen informed.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
