OL,7,FThe PPS confirmed that court papers
OL,8,Fare being finalised and a date for the
OL,9,Fdefendant's first appearance is yet to
OL,10,Fbe set.
OL,12,FIt stated that it did not wish to say
OL,13,Fanything that might prejudice
OL,14,Fproceedings and will not be making any
OL,15,Ffurther comment on this case.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
