OL,7,FThe PPS has also issued a decision in
OL,8,Frelation to a separate police
OL,9,Finvestigation reporting one civilian
OL,10,Ffor an assault on police during the
OL,11,Fincident on the Ormeau Road on
OL,12,FFebruary 5, 2021.
OL,14,FIt was determined that there is
OL,15,Finsufficient evidence to provide a
OL,16,Freasonable prospect of conviction and
OL,17,Fthe test for prosecution was not met.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
