OL,7,FThe PPS said "decision-making on both
OL,8,Ffiles was undertaken independently,
OL,9,Fimpartially and in line with the Code
OL,10,Ffor Prosecutors".
OL,12,FIn a statement, the PSNI said:
OL,13,F"Prosecutorial decisions are a matter
OL,14,Ffor the Public Prosecution Service. As
OL,15,Fthis is subject to ongoing legal
OL,16,Fproceedings we will not be commenting
OL,17,Ffurther at this time.
OL,19,F"The duty status of the officer will
OL,20,Fnow be reviewed in light of the PPS
OL,21,Fdecision."
